yTime":"2017-08-05T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>夜晚啲牛會出曬黎吹風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛牛食完飯都要散下步架</blockquote><br />\n講到牛牛 我真係要講兩句<br />\n<br />\n兩年前係梅窩沙灘食完飯同女女吹海風<br />\n見到一群牛就上前撚下<br />\n當時手上有個🍎 我拎住🍎問隻🐂<br />\n🐂🐂呀 我請你食個🍎 你俾我騎一陣得唔得丫？<br />\n話口未完 佢一啖食左個🍎<br />\n咁我地咪順勢騎上🐂🐂吹風<br />\n最後係沙灘兜左一但圈先放低我地<br />\n<br />\n🐂🐂真係好有靈性嘅動物😭😭<br />\n大家唔好再食牛 我都開始戒&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n係真唔係呀，等我到時試下先"},{"pid":"d410cdc20b891372f0c407d2ad1ad84359d4b0e6","tid":345750,"uid":13260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"買左人壽未"},{"pid":"99d7ff2fd9106cce2d661469fa91eca55b2d0a2e","tid":345750,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:38:51.000Z","msg":"咁可以留意下新聞, 睇下邊個傻仔俾牛撞"},{"pid":"b4600364134d6f8c2824563e5b2c73988179b5ca","tid":345750,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係梅窩做<br />\n其實悶到爆<br />\n冇野食冇野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做社工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n營地職員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a562ce72c0d4b6e126b34854007a4d93c10afc3","tid":345750,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"咁都算旅遊咩"}]}